::KitKat::
She raised her head as she heard the noise of the crash outside.  She 
wiped her face and stood up.  She went over and hugged 
Drillbit. "Just tell me I did the right thing."
She tried to smile and look at him.

She knew in order to be a good leader of the Predacons, she would 
have to put her own feelings aside and deal with what had to be 
done.  She looked at the door, then back at Drillbit.  "I have to go 
see what caused the noise outside.  If it was a missle or what.  Want 
to join?"  She hugged him again and didn't want to let go, but she 
knew she had to go check what happened outside the base.
